    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简介</strong></h2><br>欢迎来到《空境奇旅》——这是一款战术角色扮演游戏，结合了肉鸽玩法和桌游式的回合制战斗。运用各式各样的技能，探索难以忘怀的绝景，做出明智的选择，击退侵袭而来的暗影。当事态越发严峻时，召集盟友与你并肩作战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/5e7c8c08d65bf0b986e39e22f88038cf.avif?t=1711714084\" width=616 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游玩体验</strong></h2><br>在《空境奇旅》中，每次荒野冒险都是独一无二的。无论是独自前往还是与伙伴同行，你的决策、变化无常的命运以及神秘存在的影响都将塑造你的整个旅程。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>独特的美术风格</strong>：穿越手工绘制的七大区域，感受其独特的氛围、音乐和故事情节，带给你真正沉浸式的体验。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/3ae7439765dd923a945261ed02df6b57.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/3ae7439765dd923a945261ed02df6b57.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/3ae7439765dd923a945261ed02df6b57.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>战术回合制战斗</strong>：与怪物展开战术回合制的战斗。利用敌人的弱点，合理使用技能，在正确的时机释放力量并最终取得胜利。战斗，死亡，并在陨落灵魂的陪伴之下变得更加强大。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/d6b29a0f94ed9f4769d51c57e2c90a33.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/d6b29a0f94ed9f4769d51c57e2c90a33.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/d6b29a0f94ed9f4769d51c57e2c90a33.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>个性化技能</strong>：根据你的选择为角色学习新技能和新能力，为更多样化、更具深度的战斗提供了可能。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/85b45cdbc516c656f4fc77d5824ef5dc.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/85b45cdbc516c656f4fc77d5824ef5dc.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/85b45cdbc516c656f4fc77d5824ef5dc.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>选择前进的方向</strong>: 难以预测的随机事件将贯穿着你的旅程，是相遇、机会还是危险？明智地选择前路，它将深刻地影响整个故事。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/68a343a28351bee85c2d71961612add6.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/68a343a28351bee85c2d71961612add6.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/68a343a28351bee85c2d71961612add6.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>多角色共斗</strong>：组建一个由四名角色组成的队伍，面对更严峻的荒野挑战！合作共存，或者为了生存而做出牺牲…</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/25408409b6e96324af5c06f9db4384c2.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/25408409b6e96324af5c06f9db4384c2.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/25408409b6e96324af5c06f9db4384c2.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>与时间赛跑</strong>：时间至关重要，贪婪的暗影会不断地追逐你。保持一步领先，时刻调整策略，逃离迫近的暗影。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/c670eae8b27f5ae441dde791677790b3.poster.avif?t=1711714084\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/c670eae8b27f5ae441dde791677790b3.webm?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1786010/extras/c670eae8b27f5ae441dde791677790b3.mp4?t=1711714084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
